 my favorite things about working on ''Glory Daze'' is getting to wear amazing ''80s outfits coupled with fabulously over-the-top hair and makeup. My wardrobe usually consists of colorful sweaters, denim skirts, high-waisted shorts, crop tops, dangly earrings, jean jackets, and, of course, panty hose and shoulder pads.', 73199, 0), (460181, 'Adrenaline is an amazing thing.', 73200, 0), (460182, 'Television has changed. There''s obviously the generic shows, but on HBO and AMC, there are some really great series, so I''m not closed off to television. If there''s an amazing role with amazing people and a great story, I''d definitely be open to it.', 68119, 0), (460183, 'Music has always been in my family, but it was mainly keyboards. I learned to play classical piano, but when I first heard the amazing bass guitar of James Jamerson, who played on all the big Motown hits of the ''60s and ''70s, I knew bass guitar was my instrument.', 67772, 0), (460184, 'For such a small country, Britain packs in an amazing diversity of landscapes: coastline, lakes, mountains, rolling countryside, villages and great cities.', 68788, 0), (460185, 'It''s amazing, coconut oil. I use it as a moisturizer. I put it in my hair when I want a kind of greasy look. I take off my makeup with it. I put a little bit in my coffee. I have coconut oil with everything.', 73201, 0), (460186, 'If you ever have a kid who doesn''t know what to do, stick him in art school. It''s amazing what evolves.', 68428, 0), (460187, 'My son is wonderful. He is amazing.', 69325, 0), (460188, 'Anything salty and crunch is a world of perfection to me. Put chips in front of me, and I will eat to the bottom of the bag. Because I have the tendency to do this, I found these amazing Eden Brown Rice Chips. They''re the perfect amount of salt and crunch, and there''s nothing in them.', 73202, 0), (460189, 'When a translation is very good, it is fascinating to see how the book changes and yet stays the same. I think ''Out Stealing