 was my first record and you had Michael Jackson, Ted Ross, Nipsey Russell and Diana Ross on it. I even took it to show and tell in third grade!', 70444, 0), (460330, 'Our minds do understand that people of all races find genuine love in many places. We dig that the world is full of amazing options.', 70444, 0), (460331, 'I think Freddie Mercury is probably the best of all time in terms of a rock voice. There was a vulnerability to it, his technical ability was amazing, and so much of his personality would come out through his voice. I''m not even a guy to buy Queen records, really, and I still think he''s one of the best.', 49828, 0), (460332, 'Cotton candy is the most amazing form of caramelization ever invented by man.', 67848, 0), (460333, 'Dorado Beach''s rich history provided amazing inspiration to put forward a bold menu celebrating the legacy of the people and cuisine that shaped this unique destination and to push me to share some of my own stories.', 67848, 0), (460334, 'I have an amazing wife and three daughters that always keep me motivated.', 67848, 0), (460335, 'If you''re a basketball player and you don''t stop and take pictures with your fans, you can have an amazing game and everyone still loves you.', 34530, 0), (460336, 'It''s time you stop thinking that because you did something, it''s... amazing. All you''ve got to do is say, ''OK. If I''m great, what do they call Steve Jobs?''', 33596, 0), (460337, 'I doubt I''ll ever pay someone to do a remix again, because there''s some amazing stuff just coming out of bedrooms.', 60178, 0), (460338, 'The specific steps for changing a specific habit differ from person to person and habit to habit, but the steps - the formula - is essentially the same, and once you learn it, you can do amazing things.', 11321, 0), (460339, 'There is such amazing talent at Disney. My job is 100% creative, and I am very excited to creatively lead them.', 68139, 0), (460340, '''Bambi'' is an amazing film, and when you watch it to